  "reference_number": "RUS1738",
  "remarks": "\nZAVOD ELEKON is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. ZAVOD ELEKON is a privately owned manufacturing company specialising in the design and manufacture of electrical connectors, and supplies the Russian defence sector. ZAVOD ELEKON therefore makes available goods or technology that could contribute to destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
